quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  54,41,Aur aal-e-Firoun ke paas bhi tambihaat aayi thi
  54,42,Magar unhon ne hamari saari nishaniyon ko jhutla diya. Aakhir ko humne unhein pakda jis taraah koi zabardast qudrat wala pakadta hai
  54,43,Kya tumhare kuffar kuch un logon se behtar hain? Ya aasmani kitaabon mein tumhare liye koi maafi likhi hui hai
  54,44,"Ya in logon ka kehna yeh hai ke hum ek mazboot jattha (jamaat) hain, apna bachao kar lengey"
  54,45,Ankareeb yeh jattha(jamaat) shikhast kha jayega aur yeh sab peeth pheir kar bhaagte nazar aayenge
  54,46,Balke insey nimatne ke liye asal waade ka waqt to qayamat hai aur woh badi aafat aur zyaada talkh-saa-at (badi sakht aur kadwi cheez) hai
  54,47,Yeh mujrim log dar haqeeqat galat fehmi mein mubtala hain aur inki aqal maari gayi hai
  54,48,Jis roz yeh mooh ke bal aag mein ghaseetey jayenge us roz insey kaha jayega ke ab chakkho jahannum ki lapat ka maza
  54,49,Humne har cheez ek taqdeer ke saath paida ki hai
  54,50,Aur hamara hukum bas ek hi hukum hota hai aur palak jhapakate (twinkling of an eye) woh amal mein aa jata hai
  54,51,Tum jaisey bahut-soon ko hum halak kar chuke hain. Phir hai koi nasihat qabool karne wala
  54,52,Jo kuch inhon ne kiya hai woh sab daftaron (office) mein darj hai
  54,53,Aur har choti badi baat likhi hui maujood hai
  54,54,Nafarmani se parhez karne waley yaqeenan baaghon aur neharon mein hongey
  54,55,"Sacchi izzat ki jagah, badey zeeh-iqtedar baadshah ke kareeb"